<p>FREE PARKING FOR DISABLED BADGE HOLDERS.  Upto 1 hour £1.80  1-2 hrs £3  2-4 hrs £4  4-8 hrs £5  8-24 hrs £10   Concessions are available for visitors of long-stay inpatients or patients attending for long-term treatment. £10 for 5 days  £12 for 7 days  Contact the ward for details.  Car parking machines do not give change and we cannot guarantee a parking space.</p>
